replies.body:
I could imagine that would feel pretty terrible if you carried the entire the match. I'm not sure what happened in your match, but just carrying the match doesn't entitle you to honors. The Vayne may have done something the team really liked and you can't sway their opinions on that. If everyone honored someone on your team though, then you'll get hit with a little more of that sweet sweet honor! 

Sounds like you're on the right track though, so don't let one game discourage you. If you play positively then those honors will stack up for you! 

{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}
